  abstract  = {We propose AC-DiT, an end-to-end vision-language-action model framework for mobile manipulation. It features a two-stage action generation mechanism (coarse prediction + diffusion refinement) and achieves significantly better performance on multiple benchmarks and real-robot experiments compared to existing methods.},
